Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.24,0:00:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What if your deepest regrets manifested as something terrifying?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.13,0:00:13.43,Default,,0,0,0,,A group was told to stay put, tasked with tending to the sick, but fear held them captive.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.75,0:00:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,One of them, a specter, emerged, an effigy of Sebastian sent to Lure Helen.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.80,0:00:26.35,Default,,0,0,0,,This ghost rallied more spectres fueled by the guilt of the people of New Eden.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.66,0:00:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It was the anguish of the dead, their suffering twisted by a cruel leader's denial.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.34,0:00:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,He chose to inflict pain on others rather than confront his own darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.03,0:00:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Will this cycle of torment ever end?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.09,0:00:46.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What truly unleashed the darkness upon New Eden?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.29,0:00:51.09,Default,,0,0,0,,A woman cried out, bound in chains, her pleas ignored.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.19,0:00:56.93,Default,,0,0,0,,This silence ignited a curse, a creeping dread that gripped the town.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.13,0:01:03.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Years later, a tragedy struck the mind, a disaster whispered to be her vengeful act.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.71,0:01:08.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, a leader is needed, one untainted by this dark past.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.65,0:01:16.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Yet the path back to New Eden is blocked, the town consumed by fear and hatred for what it cannot comprehend.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.63,0:01:21.61,Default,,0,0,0,,The only hope lies in finding answers, perhaps from a woman named Grace,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.73,0:01:25.37,Default,,0,0,0,,and laying the past to rest before the void claims them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.43,0:01:29.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What forgotten sin still haunts New Eden?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.00,0:01:33.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Did she send him into the woods to die?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.48,0:01:38.04,Default,,0,0,0,,He sought a hidden treasure, a fortune promised by old maps,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.34,0:01:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,but the land yielded only rot and despair.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.46,0:01:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,His brother claimed the prize,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.42,0:01:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,a act of betrayal that sealed his fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.72,0:01:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Now a dark ritual looms.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.86,0:01:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,What truly happened in that cursed cabin, and who is grace,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.30,0:01:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,is the teacher a phantom or a manipulator.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.10,0:02:04.14,Default,,0,0,0,,The camp trembles, threatened by a past that refuses to stay buried.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.36,0:02:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What secrets lie within those woods?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.20,0:02:08.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell us your theories below.